{"TopicId":195096,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Extendable harpoon for comet landings","CreatedByName":"EchoLima","CreatedById":61992,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-27T18:40:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"EchoLima","CreatedById":61992,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-27T18:40:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe obvious comet mission to recreate in 1.10 is Rosetta. Assuming a 2.5m Ariane V, Rosetta would probably be 1.25m, and the tiny Philae lander .625m. The lander needs a way to grapple to the comet, and while the new Klaw Jr is nice, even that is too bulky when attached to probe core of the same size.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ACtC-3dVfqLNHksUmeZ0TicKP9wPUIFJyNKcIXoN\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002246.19\u0022 height=\u0022554\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ACtC-3dVfqLNHksUmeZ0TicKP9wPUIFJyNKcIXoNDKnE7bBnyf61zNaIDfeZaASagStASrTAat4iVxGTZK7nhyJr96rK32Qp4JIX4TH3FHhXmXtspA3f0-0TnlaqWeUYJs0ZcSbLWBzc1Z6EnEUGdiCg-d-JMw=w1442-h669-no\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EMy Philae recreation, using the Klaw Jr from Restock\u002B. It had to be clipped into the probe to not appear so large, but then it wouldn\u0027t work properly.\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstead, we should also get a surface attachble harpoon (just like Philae had), similar in size to the commutron 16. When extended, it would insert into the comet/object and attach like a klaw. This would be much more versatile as it could be used with tiny spacecraft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-06-27T18:45:01Z\u0022 title=\u002206/27/2020 06:45  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJune 27, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by EchoLima\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-28T12:20:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Zgm0XP0YqAc?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xurkitree","CreatedById":187694,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-06-28T14:59:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223810610\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022195096\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221593283218\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002261992\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022EchoLima\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 hours ago, EchoLima said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[snip]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou should probably look at Shadowzone\u0027s video of the comet mission included with the game. That would give a more accurate idea of what the KSP team\u0027s idea of Philae grabbing the comet looks like.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}